						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying near the Ānjanēya temple.</p>						

						<p>ŚRĪ VEṄKṬAPATIDĒVA MAHĀRĀYA.</p>						

						<p>1640 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated Śaka 1592, Naḷa (wrong for Sādhāraṇa), Bhādrapada, śu. 15, Irregular.</p>						

						<p>Fragmentary and incomplete. Mentions the king <hi rend="italic">rājādhirāja, rājaparamēśvara</hi> Śrī Vīravenkaṭadēva mahārāya.</p>						

